T = int(input())
for i in range(0, T):
    (N, B) = map(int, input().split())
    W = []
    H = []
    P = []
    area = []
    search = []
    final = []
    count = 0
    for i in range(0, N):
        (a, b, c) = map(int, input().split())
        W.append(a)
        H.append(b)
        P.append(c)
        x = a * b
        area.append(x)
    for j in range(0, N):
        if P[j] <= B:
            search.append(j)
            count = count + 1
            final.append(area[j])
    if count > 0:
        print(max(final))
    else:
        print('no tablet')

t = int(input())
for i in range(t):
    x = []
    y = []
    z = []
    l = []
    m = []
    (n, b) = map(int, input().split())
    for j in range(n):
        (w, h, p) = map(int, input().split())
        x.append(w)
        y.append(h)
        z.append(p)
        if z[j] <= b:
            l.append(z[j])
            m.append(x[j] * y[j])
    if len(m) == 0:
        print('no tablet')
    else:
        print(max(m))
